{{Infobox university school | name = School of Science | parent = [[RMIT University]] College of Science, Engineering and Health | image = | head_label = Executive Dean | head = Russell Crawford<ref>[http://www.rmit.edu.au/about/our-education/academic-schools/science/contact/people People]. School of Science, [[RMIT University]]. Retrieved 24 October 2017</ref> | campus = [[RMIT City|City]], Bundoora | affiliations = | website = [http://www.rmit.edu.au/about/our-education/academic-schools/science School of Science] }}
